title: Independent Candidate Javed Imran wins PK-113 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): An Independent Candidate Javed Imran has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK 113, D.I.Khan-III by securing 4,200 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an Tehreek-e-Labaik Pakistan (TLP) candidate Haji Muhammad Aqeel who bagged 1,270 votes.
Overall voters turn-out remained 45.25 per cent.
